originalText.text:
Dr. Goldman is the kind of psychiatrist that people mean when they say how important it is to find a qualified, "good" psychiatrist.  He's not only good - he is exemplary.  Extremely insightful. He has a way of asking the right questions and making the right comments that somehow bring you to the place and the answer that you were trying to find. His demeanor is kind and there is no such thing as judgement.  He has helped me be my best self built on a foundation of found courage, and strength I didn't know I had, navigated with his strong, simple, honest. straight, calm support.

Also his office is entirely private, high end and extremely comfortable with a gorgeous view.
